## The Anniversary Ring Price Guide: Budget by Milestone

Anniversary ring budget tends to correspond to the significance of the milestone. A practical framework:

**1st Anniversary ($825–$1,100):** Floating diamond or entry pavé. [Floating Diamond Yellow Gold at $825](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/floating-diamond-wedding-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-3-ct-tw-item-192376?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the most affordable meaningful option. The [Riviera Pavé 14k White Gold 1/6 ct at $980](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/riviera-pave-diamond-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-6-ct-tw-item-194923?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the clean entry pavé choice.

**5th Anniversary ($1,100–$1,420):** Upgrade to more diamond coverage. [Riviera Pavé 14k White Gold 1/4 ct at $1,100](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/riviera-pave-diamond-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-195256?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) or [Riviera Pavé Platinum 1/4 ct at $1,420](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/riviera-pave-diamond-ring-in-platinum-1-4-ct-tw-item-194988?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for the platinum upgrade.

**10th Anniversary ($1,600–$3,000):** Statement pavé or upgrade pavé in platinum. This is when a second stack band (making it a 3-ring stack: engagement + original wedding band + anniversary band) becomes appropriate.

**25th Anniversary ($3,000+):** Full eternity band or a significant stack upgrade. The [Bold Diamond Eternity at $4,305](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/bold-diamond-eternity-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-7-mm-1-2-ct-tw-item-147440?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the top tier available on Blue Nile.

